881
01:40:48,918 --> 01:40:49,999
Right, Calo?

882
01:40:50,086 --> 01:40:51,201
(REPEATING IN ITALIAN)

883
01:40:53,673 --> 01:40:55,664
Such hair, such mouth!

884
01:40:58,094 --> 01:41:01,337
The girls around here are
beautiful... but virtuous.

885
01:41:01,806 --> 01:41:04,264
This one had a purple dress...

886
01:41:04,475 --> 01:41:06,637
And a purple ribbon in her hair.

887
01:41:07,478 --> 01:41:10,687
A type more Greek than Italian.

888
01:41:11,649 --> 01:41:12,684
(REPEATING)

889
01:41:13,234 --> 01:41:14,645
Do you know her?

890
01:41:19,532 --> 01:41:22,274
There's no girl like that
in this town.

891
01:41:24,912 --> 01:41:26,152
My God, I understand!

892
01:41:26,330 --> 01:41:28,492
(OWNER SHOUTING IN ITALIAN)

893
01:41:30,293 --> 01:41:31,328
What's wrong?

894
01:41:33,546 --> 01:41:34,832
Let's go.

895
01:41:36,716 --> 01:41:38,081
It's his daughter.

896
01:41:38,676 --> 01:41:40,041
Tell him to come here.

897
01:41:43,514 --> 01:41:44,675
Call him.

898
01:41:55,484 --> 01:41:57,566
(MEN CHATTERING IN ITALIAN)

899
01:42:04,744 --> 01:42:07,156
Fabrizio, you translate.

900
01:42:11,334 --> 01:42:12,995
I apologize if I offended you.

901
01:42:13,127 --> 01:42:14,162
(TRANSLATING IN ITALIAN)

902
01:42:14,295 --> 01:42:17,504
I'm a stranger in this country.

903
01:42:17,590 --> 01:42:20,708
I meant no disrespect
to you or your daughter.

904
01:42:26,307 --> 01:42:29,140
I'm an American, hiding in Sicily.

905
01:42:30,645 --> 01:42:32,761
My name is Michael Corleone.

906
01:42:34,857 --> 01:42:38,976
There are people who'd pay
a lot of money for that information.

907
01:42:41,197 --> 01:42:44,315
But then your daughter
would lose a father

908
01:42:45,743 --> 01:42:48,235
instead of gaining a husband.

909
01:42:56,420 --> 01:42:58,707
I want to meet your daughter.

910
01:42:59,298 --> 01:43:03,758
With your permission, and under
the supervision of your family.

911
01:43:04,595 --> 01:43:06,177
With all respect.

912
01:43:12,228 --> 01:43:16,267
(IN ITALIAN) Come to my house
Sunday morning. My name is Vitelli.

913
01:43:21,654 --> 01:43:23,270
(IN ITALIAN) What's her name?

914
01:43:24,782 --> 01:43:26,193
Apollonia.

915
01:43:54,729 --> 01:43:56,720
(VITELLI SPEAKING IN ITALIAN)

916
01:44:43,778 --> 01:44:45,610
(SPEAKING ITALIAN)

917
01:44:54,497 --> 01:44:55,862
(BELL TOLLING)

918
01:44:58,083 --> 01:44:59,949
(CHATTERING IN ITALIAN)

919
01:45:39,458 --> 01:45:41,040
(WOMEN CHATTERING)

920
01:45:53,472 --> 01:45:54,837
(COIN CLINKING)

