930
01:47:14,929 --> 01:47:18,342
I'm just going to get a doctor
to take a look at you.

931
01:47:18,474 --> 01:47:21,011
Sonny, please don't do anything.

932
01:47:22,978 --> 01:47:24,938
What's the matter with you?
What am I going to do?

933
01:47:24,980 --> 01:47:28,018
Make that baby an orphan
before he's born?

934
01:47:32,488 --> 01:47:35,776
You spic slobs still betting Yankees?

935
01:47:35,908 --> 01:47:37,774
